es, to indicate whether they succeeded or failed. Other functions return a calculated or selected value. Other functions return nothing (we’ll see examples of these in the next lesson).Because of the wide variety of possibilities here, it’s a good idea to document your function with a comment indicating what the return values mean. For example:// Function asks user to enter a value
